Great that you are putting in effort to deliver under these circumstances. However, it would be great if parcel would actually be delivered and not just marked as delivered when looking at the shipment tracking it's impossible that the parcel could have been delivered at the time indicated. According to shipment, the parcel was put into the delivery car in the same minute it was delivered to me. In addition, just a few hours earlier it was in a completely different part of Germany and could not have arrived at our region in the time given. And the worst part is that neither I nor the sending company are given more information by @dhl_global than what we already know from the tracking status. Nobody feels responsible to look into what happened. @dhl_global should be able to see exactly who allegedly delivered the package and should be able to see that this person doesn't even work in the region I live in. What @dhl_global is doing is not doing their job and customer support is also not a service they can be proud of! I'm going to try and send packages with our delivery companies in the future!

I am a proud owner of DebbieTol Store on Etsy with over 220 sales and all 95% of these orders were delivered all around the globe via DHL. My recent experience with DHL made me forget all the successful deliveries during the years because i sent an order to a buyer in Florida, United States from Nigeria; 4 days later i received a notification that it was delivered and i thought i would get a 5 star review from my buyer for a job well done just to get a message from her that it wasn't delivered. I attacked her after receiving proof of delivery from DHL that she signed for delivery because i had some bad experience of buyer telling lies just to get a refund. I trusted DHL which i shouldn't. We both contacted DHL and they promised to look into it, that was when i knew something was off. I sent her a message days later to get an update from her and she explained angrily how DHL delivered to a wrong address and left it on the person's front porch, her order was later delivered few days later while apologising to her but don't i deserve an apology? She threatened to give a bad review and report my store, in fact my store is now suspended but can i blame her? No, i blame DHL. Which should your mistake cause me my livelihood? Your company hurt mine but you carry on
